text: Katie McKenty (born 30 January 1996) is a New Zealand water polo player. She has competed for the New Zealand women's national water polo team in the 2019, 2022, 2023 and 2024 World Aquatics Championships. She was educated at Takapuna Grammar School. She played for Hartwick College's women's water polo team. == References == == Other websites == * womens-water-polo-hartwick * broken- trust-hartwick-college * hartwick-board-to-womens-water-polo Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:New Zealand water polo players
